[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    416[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;192;197;206mOriginal (grade 14):[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    417[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;208;135;112m>[38;2;208;135;112m "Patient experienced acute ST-elevation myocardial infarction with subsequent percutaneous coronary intervention via drug-eluting stent placement in the LAD. Continue dual antiplatelet therapy: aspirin 81mg and clopidogrel 75mg daily for 12 months. Avoid NSAIDs. Follow up with cardiology in 2 weeks."[K
